components.name: Extract User from API
components.description: Fetches user JSON from the external ReqRes API endpoint using the configured HTTP connection and pushes the raw response to XCom.

upstream_policy.description: No upstream dependencies; this is the first task in the DAG.

connections.purpose: HTTP GET request to fetch user data

components.name: Process User Data
components.description: Parses the raw JSON from the API, extracts firstname, lastname and email fields, and pushes the processed data to XCom for downstream use.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after successful completion of extract_user_api.

components.name: Create User Table
components.description: Executes a DDL statement via PostgresOperator to create the 'users' table with columns for firstname, lastname, and email.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after successful completion of process_user_data.

connections.purpose: Execute DDL to create the users table

components.name: Insert User Data
components.description: Inserts the processed user fields into the previously created PostgreSQL 'users' table using a templated INSERT statement.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after successful completion of both process_user_data and create_user_table.

connections.purpose: Insert processed user record into the users table

description.description: Pipeline that fetches user data from an external API, processes it, creates a PostgreSQL table, and inserts the processed data.
